{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe512202b6","title":"给外国专家局的大字报：为什么在世界革命的心脏工作的外国人被推上修正主义的道路？？？","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dcc304ccc0","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":31,"articleId":"fe512202b6","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"641da03de1","name":"美国在华专家  阳早"},{"id":"8c10841240","name":"美国在华专家  史克"},{"id":"b1d75b8317","name":"美国在华专家  汤普金斯"},{"id":"b48fb8710e","name":"美国在华专家  寒春"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"15d359791d","type":"title","text":"给外国专家局的大字报：为什么在世界革命的心脏工作的外国人被推上修正主义的道路？？？","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e79f565c3e","type":"paragraph","text":"是哪个牛鬼蛇神指使给外国人这种待遇？在中国工作的外国人，不论他是哪个阶级，不论他对革命是什么态度，都受到这种“五无二有”的待遇：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d02401689c","type":"paragraph","text":"“五无”：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"188437e50f","type":"paragraph","text":"一，没有体力劳动；","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4ee3eb5b62","type":"paragraph","text":"二，没有思想改造；","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5630f9a12","type":"paragraph","text":"三，没有接触工农兵机会；","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a240d3b1f2","type":"paragraph","text":"四，不搞阶级斗争；","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62fa082eaf","type":"paragraph","text":"五，不搞生产斗争。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f477d4fad0","type":"paragraph","text":"“二有”：","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"89d16188c0","type":"paragraph","text":"一，有特高生活待遇；","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dba981e128","type":"paragraph","text":"二，有各方面的特殊化。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e9441c5037","type":"paragraph","text":"制定这种待遇是什么思想支配的？这不是毛泽东思想，这是赫鲁晓夫思想，是修正主义的思想，这是剥削阶级思想。这样做的目的是什么？结果又是什么呢？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf7e83d73a","type":"paragraph","text":"1.使要革命的外国人不能掌握毛泽东思想，只能在口头上说条条；","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9345c620f3","type":"paragraph","text":"2.使革命的外国人革命意志衰退，滑到修正主义道路上去；","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f9281da8e4","type":"paragraph","text":"3.阻碍在中国的外国小孩成长为坚强的革命者；","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cd90c25f6a","type":"paragraph","text":"4.把革命的外国人和他们的中国阶级兄弟隔离开，破坏他们的阶级感情，破坏无产阶级国际主义。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3c46466031","type":"paragraph","text":"我们认为这不是个别人的问题，而是关系到世界革命的原则的问题，我们坚决反对这种待遇。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28f266bc2a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们决心要成为坚强的革命者，成为坚定的反修战士。为了把反对美帝国主义的斗争进行到底，我们决心锻炼和考验我们自己。我们的后代必须成为坚强可靠的革命接班人，而决不允许他们变成修正主义分子。因此我们要求：","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b23bb9bd13","type":"paragraph","text":"1.以阶级兄弟看待我们，而不是以资产阶级专家看待我们；","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5627e0eddd","type":"paragraph","text":"2.允许并鼓励我们参加体力劳动；","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2eb7700699","type":"paragraph","text":"3.帮助我们进行思想改造；","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d27d2672a3","type":"paragraph","text":"4.允许并鼓励我们紧密地结合工农群众；","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3caa409e1b","type":"paragraph","text":"5.允许并鼓励我们参加三大革命运动；","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"48dd0cc11d","type":"paragraph","text":"6.我们的孩子和中国的孩子，受到同样的待遇和严格的要求；","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"274b38783e","type":"paragraph","text":"7.生活待遇和同级的中国工作人员一样；","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df13486b28","type":"paragraph","text":"8.取消特殊化。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3bcb19738a","type":"paragraph","text":"只有这样，我们才有可能成为毛主席所要求的革命者。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d06b19d75a","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的无产阶级文化大革命万岁！","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"343b04b534","type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民大团结万岁！","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"039bd3ebc6","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的战无不胜的毛泽东思想万岁！","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b84d9ad9ce","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民、世界无产阶级及被压迫人民、被压迫民族的伟大领袖毛泽东同志万岁！万万岁！！","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"fe512202b6","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}